data.description: Very attractive 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom townhouse located in the great, gated community of The Villas of Lake Washington! This home boast a large kitchen with corian countertops that seamlessly opens into the family room and dining area. The three spacious bedrooms are upstairs and one half bath is downstairs for guests. This unit comes with its own 1 car garage. The roof was just done last year and a new AC was installed last year as well. The Villas of Lake Washington are centrally located within a short ride to the beach, Patrick SFB, shopping and 95. It also boats a community pool, rec center and a playground. Come see this gorgeous townhome today!
